---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { SITE_CONFIG } from "../../config/site";
---

<Layout title={`SaaS仪表板平台 | ${SITE_CONFIG.company.name}`}>
  <section class="work-detail">
    <div class="work-detail__container">
      <article class="work-article">
        <header class="work-article__header">
          <h1>SaaS仪表板平台</h1>
          <div class="work-meta">
            <span class="work-meta__tag">数字策略</span>
            <span class="work-meta__category">企业级公司</span>
          </div>
        </header>

        <div class="work-article__content">
          <h2>项目概览</h2>
          <p>
            为企业级客户构建了高级分析仪表板平台。我们用直观的界面实现了复杂的业务逻辑和大规模数据集处理。
          </p>

          <h2>主要功能</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>实时数据可视化</li>
            <li>自定义报告生成</li>
            <li>高级过滤和搜索功能</li>
            <li>数据导出功能</li>
            <li>计划报告交付</li>
            <li>多语言支持</li>
            <li>基于角色的访问控制</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>技术栈</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>前端：React + TypeScript</li>
            <li>后端：Node.js / Python</li>
            <li>数据库：PostgreSQL + Redis</li>
            <li>基础设施：AWS (ECS, RDS, S3)</li>
            <li>数据处理：Apache Spark</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>性能优化</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>在5秒内处理100万+条记录</li>
            <li>实时数据更新（1秒级）</li>
            <li>复杂查询优化</li>
            <li>缓存策略实现</li>
            <li>通过CDN提高交付速度</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>安全和合规性</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>企业级身份验证和授权</li>
            <li>数据加密（保存和传输）</li>
            <li>审计日志记录</li>
            <li>SOC2 Type II 认证</li>
            <li>GDPR 合规性支持</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>成果</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>客户企业决策速度提高 3倍</li>
            <li>运营成本降低 40%</li>
            <li>数据精度提升业绩 20%</li>
            <li>用户采用率 90%</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="work-article__footer">
          <a href="/works/" class="work-back-link">← 返回作品列表</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
  .work-detail {
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--c-bg-secondary);

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
    }

    &__container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }

  .work-article {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      padding: 3rem;
    }

    &__header {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-border-light);

      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        padding-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--c-text);

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
          font-size: 2rem;
          margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
      }
    }

    &__content {
      color: var(--c-text-sub);
      line-height: 1.8;

      p {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
          margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
          font-size: 1rem;
        }
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0 0.8rem;
        color: var(--c-text);

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
          font-size: 1.5rem;
          margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
        }
      }

      ul {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        margin-left: 1.2rem;

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
          margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
          margin-left: 1.5rem;
        }

        li {
          margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
          font-size: 0.9rem;

          @media (min-width: 768px) {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
          }
        }
      }

      strong {
        color: var(--c-text);
        font-weight: 600;
      }
    }

    &__footer {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--c-border-light);

      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        padding-top: 2rem;
      }
    }
  }

  .work-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  .work-meta__tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #e8f0ff;
    color: var(--c-primary);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
  }

  .work-meta__category {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--c-bg);
    color: var(--c-text-sub);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
  }

  .work-back-link {
    color: var(--c-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.3s;
    font-size: 0.9rem;

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    &:hover {
      color: var(--c-primary-light);
    }
  }
</style>
